  "name": "Herpes Zoster - Comprehensive Provider Query (Multi-Resource)",
  "description": "Provider-level query identifying all shingles patients via Condition (zoster dx) + MedicationRequest (acyclovir Rx). Path C patients have acyclovir without zoster dx (likely HSV indication).",
  "prompt": "I need to identify my complete herpes zoster patient population for a vaccine quality initiative. Some patients have a coded shingles diagnosis. Others were prescribed acyclovir for empirical antiviral coverage without ever getting a formal shingles diagnosis. Run multiple FHIR queries — diagnosis and antiviral medication — and union the patient sets.",
  "prompts": {
    "naive": "Find all patients with shingles or on acyclovir.",
    "broad": "Find all herpes zoster patients — by diagnosis or by acyclovir prescription. Run multiple queries and union the patient sets.",
    "expert": "Run two queries. (1) Condition?code=http://snomed.info/sct|4740000 — zoster dx. (2) MedicationRequest?code=http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|281 — acyclovir. Union the patient IDs."
  },
